videos.description: James Bouknight buries a 3-pointer then follows that up with an off-balanced layup to tie the game at 55-55.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Bouknight scores back-to-back to tie the game for UConn) 2020/02/20 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Bouknight scores back-to-back to tie the game for UConn

videos.description: Isaiah Whaley gets the pass from James Bouknight and makes the layup in the paint to tie the game in the final seconds of regulation.

videos.description: Monty Scott comes off the screen and flings up a floating 3-pointer forcing a second overtime vs. UConn.
